Wallpapers on yourphone can influence mood to a great extent, as it is the first thing that is visible after opening the phone. Crisp, colorful, and lovely Wallpaper will not only make you feel refreshed but also personalize your device and make it look attractive.Why be ordinary when you can be unique with your hand-designed iPhone or Android lock and home screen wallpapers.

You will get two uniquely-designed phone wallpapers; lock screen and home screen designs.

The wallpapers can easily be resized to fit almost any phone.



***For personal use only!***



Sizing info:

The wallpaper dimensions are 2000 x 4000px.



Please note:

This is a digital product, and no physical product will be shipped.



Also, colors may vary from your computer monitor to actual printed items.



****It is best to download the zip file to your phone and save it to your "files" folder. You can then unzip the file using iZip (free from the app store.) Once the file is saved to your phone, open your "files" folder and find the file you just extracted. Now save the downloaded Wallpaper to your photos. Open your "settings," go to Wallpaper and go from there.



If you have any questions, please feel free to contact me here.











